[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ardoyne, north Belfast: Teenager annoyed at sectarian attack

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A teenage boy has said he is "shocked and annoyed" after being assaulted in a sectarian attack in north Belfast.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
23 May 2016 Last updated at 19:21 BST
Bailey Anderson, 13, was attacked along with another 14-year-old boy on the Ardoyne Road on Saturday at about 15:00 BST.
